Developing and maintaining exisiting customers, with the objective of achieving and exceeding forecasted sales goals through networking activities, direct and online meetings with clients, distributors and prospects;
Monitor and optimise all KPIs, by identifying new opportunities and inciting creative solutions;
Ensure policies, operational standards and procedures are communicated, understood & implemented by our partners whilst also proposing any improvement actions;
